[I] A Microsoft Works file format import filter based on top of the librevenge

[T] Currently, libwps can import all word processing Works formats since
[T] about 1995 with some success. It may also be able to import some basic
[T] database and spreadsheet files.

[U] https://sourceforge.net/projects/libwps/

